#--- Capture Filters ---#

Much more restricted than display filters, used to reduce raw capture size

--- Filters (IPs)---

host 10.10.10.10 	# Capture traffic to and from this host

net 10.10.10.10/24	# Capture traffic to this range

dst net 192.168.0.0/24 	# Outbound
src net 192.168.0.0/24	# Inbound

--- Filters (ports) ---

port 53							# Capture only DNS (port 53) traffic

host www.example.com and not (port 80 or port 25)	# Skip HTTP and SMTP traffic



